<div class="content" name="WINSTATIONCREATE" uuid="dcd01340-5084-4089-8173-ad3a5831e087"><p>The <b>WINSTATIONCREATE</b> structure specifies a session to
which the user can connect.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct _WINSTATIONCREATE {
   ULONG fEnableWinStation :1;
   ULONG MaxInstanceCount;
 } WINSTATIONCREATE, * PWINSTATIONCREATE;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>fEnableWinStation:</b>  TRUE if enabled.</p><p><b>MaxInstanceCount:</b>  Maximum number of
instances that can connect to the <span><a href="c41d3367-04c9-4c93-babf-9b5de834eb29#gt_8cc89bb9-be94-4672-8a5d-9947b91bc952" data-linktype="relative-path">WinStation</a></span>.</p></div>